<title>USA: Lindsay stake raised by Bass group.</title>
<headline>Lindsay stake raised by Bass group.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>A group including members of the Bass family of Fort Worth, Texas, said Thursday it raised its stake in Lindsay Manufacturing to 1,622,397 common shares or 16.9 percent from 15.9 percent previously held.</p>
<p>In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission, the group said its latest transactions include buying 113,100 common between March 7 and May 7 at $28.13 to $32.93 a share.</p>
<p>Lindsay, based in Lindsay, Neb., makes irrigation systems and special metal products.</p>
